snippet.title: Pancake Patrol Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now and join the Pancake Patrol! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2587840/Pancake_Patrol

Embark on a pancake-fueled roguelite adventure! Defeat thousands of monsters with food-based weaponry, face bullet hell bosses, & explore diverse game modes. Choose from 10 characters, conquer Boss Rush challenges & All Out Elites, fight 1v1 boss battles, & join the Pancake Patrol for flipping fun!

Song "Microchip" by SnowMusicStudio
